item.title: Trance Refracted #14: Uplifting Return
item.description: Uplifting has returned on Trance Refracted with this power episode featuring Rising Star, TrancEye, Ferry Corsten in his alias Gouryella, Hamnoy Project and his debut track Early Stages, and a remix of Novus!
